<section class="py-8 px-4 relative z-10 w-full overflow-visible">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
        <div class="text-center mb-8 px-2">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight drop-shadow-lg">Pack Despegue Digital</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm">Todo lo que necesitas para profesionalizar tu negocio, sin letra pequeña.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full">
            
            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-orange-600 rounded-3xl blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-75 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200"></div>
                
                <div class="relative bg-[#0F0F0F]/90 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden shadow-2xl h-full">
                    
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-40 h-40 bg-primary/20 blur-[50px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

                    <div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                            <span class="text-gray-500 line-through text-lg">900€</span>
                            <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase border border-primary/20">Oferta Limitada</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2 relative z-10">
                            <span class="text-2xl text-gray-400 font-medium">desde</span>
                            <h3 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white">399€</h3>
                            <span class="text-lg text-gray-400">/ único</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6 border-b border-white/10 pb-6 relative z-10">Diseño Web Profesional a Medida</p>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm md:text-base relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-200"><span class="text-green-400 shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(74,222,128,0.5)] rounded-full">✓</span> <span>Diseño <strong>100% personalizado</strong>.</span></div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-200"><span class="text-green-400 shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(74,222,128,0.5)] rounded-full">✓</span> <span>Entrega en menos de 15 días.</span></div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-200"><span class="text-green-400 shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(74,222,128,0.5)] rounded-full">✓</span> <span><strong>4 Secciones:</strong> Inicio, Servicios, Nosotros, Contacto.</span></div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-200"><span class="text-green-400 shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(74,222,128,0.5)] rounded-full">✓</span> <span><strong>Dominio + Hosting GRATIS</strong> (1er año).</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#contacto" class="w-full bg-white text-black font-bold py-3.5 rounded-xl text-center hover:bg-gray-200 transition-transform active:scale-[0.98] shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.5)] relative z-10">Reservar Ahora</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative group">
                 <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 to-slate-600 rounded-3xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-1000"></div>

                <div class="relative bg-[#0F0F0F]/80 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-md">Incluye todo lo necesario:</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></span> Adaptado a Móvil, Tablet y PC</li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></span> Formulario de contacto</li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></span> Enlazado con Redes Sociales</li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></span> Optimización SEO</li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></span> Carga ultrarrápida</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/5 p-5 rounded-xl mt-auto flex flex-col gap-4 relative overflow-hidden group-hover:border-white/10 transition-colors">
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
                                <h4 class="text-white font-bold">Soporte 24/7 (Opcional)</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Mantenimiento técnico completo.</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg bg-black/40 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg border border-white/5">29,99€<span class="text-xs text-gray-400">/mes</span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center sm:text-left border-t border-white/10 pt-3">
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 leading-tight">
                                * Si no deseas la suscripción mensual, las actualizaciones o cambios puntuales se cobrarán a <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold">80€/intervención</span>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>